      <title>Steelmaker Posco旨在扩大美国供应量更多的液化天然气业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/steelmaker-posco-aims-to-expand-lng-business-amid-more-us-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拥有韩国顶级钢铁制造商的Posco Holdings Inc.将扩大其液化的天然气业务，以便受益于快速增长的市场和唐纳德·特朗普总统促进美国出口的战略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/steelmaker-posco-aims-to-expand-lng-business-amid-more-us-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 01:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国农民将获得300亿美元的第一款批次，以抗击经济低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/us-farmers-to-get-first-tranche-of-30-billion-to-fight-downturn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[农业秘书布鲁克·罗林斯（Brooke Rollins）表示，美国农民将很快开始获得国会批准的300亿美元资金的第一笔司机，以与市场上的低迷作斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-03/us-farmers-to-get-first-tranche-of-30-billion-to-fight-downturn</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 00:59:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
